personal_info.summary: Full-Stack Developer with experience in cybersecurity and a high ability to adapt to new technologies and challenges. Focused on React, Java, and Node.js, with experience in building scalable solutions, optimizing performance, and ensuring code quality standards.

responsibilities: Developed and managed a web platform for management and reservations, including features such as inventory control, appointment scheduling, record tracking, and a login system.
Built an intuitive and responsive user interface using Next.js, TypeScript, Redux, Tailwind, and CSS Module.
Developed the back-end using NestJS and TypeORM, integrating real-time data management and operations.
Implemented PostgreSQL as the database to securely store reservation data, inventory information, and user records.
Managed the full project lifecycle, from planning and implementation to ongoing maintenance, ensuring optimal performance and scalability.
Established work guidelines based on Clean Code and Clean Architecture to optimize the development and maintainability of the existing front-end.
Developed and optimized front-end functionalities using Next.js, Redux, Tailwind, Zustand, and Axios, contributing to an 80% increase in the customer base.
Improved user experience by collaborating with designers in Figma, achieving a drop-out rate reduction to 2%.
Developed and optimized key functionalities in the back-end using Java, Hibernate, Lombok, and PostgreSQL, achieving a 30% reduction in response times.
Supervised the code developed by the team through thorough reviews, ensuring quality and adherence to standards.
Trained new team members, facilitating their integration and aligning them with best development practices.
Used Docker for application containerization.
Utilized management tools such as Git, GitLab, Azure DevOps, Confluence, Swagger, and Asana.
Developed user interfaces with JavaScript, HTML, and CSS, ensuring a responsive and optimized user experience.
Designed and implemented APIs using C# and SQL Server.
Built microservices and managed their deployment in the cloud.
Developed scripts to automate internal processes.
Led static code analyses, identifying vulnerabilities and applying security controls to ensure application quality and protection.
Implemented security practices in the software development lifecycle, enhancing data protection and contributing to application resilience.
Collaborated on ISO 27001 compliance, helping maintain high standards of information security.
